---
title: "Risk-Tiered Component Mapping"
theme: base
themeVariables:
  primaryColor: "#a5d8ff"
  primaryBorderColor: "#4a9eed"
  lineColor: "#555"
config:
  flowchart:
    htmlLabels: true
    curve: basis
    nodeSpacing: 45
    rankSpacing: 60
---
flowchart TD
    COMP([<b>System Component</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>A distinct step in the AI processing chain</span>]):::start

    Q1{<b>Q1: Cost if wrong?</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>Severity + reversibility of the error</span>}:::question

    Q2{<b>Q2: Can human verify?</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>Check output without re-running the AI?</span>}:::question

    Q3{<b>Q3: Named accountable role?</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>One job title owns this output?</span>}:::question

    FIX[<b>Fix the Structure First</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>Add explanation / name a role, then re-evaluate</span>]:::fix

    HITL[<b>Human-in-the-Loop (HITL)</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>Blocking · Logged · Empowered · Monitored</span>]:::hitl

    HOTL[<b>Human-on-the-Loop (HOTL)</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>AI acts; human audits a sample and can intervene</span>]:::hotl

    HOOTL[<b>Human-out-of-the-Loop (HOOTL)</b><br/><span style='font-size:12px;color:#6d28d9'>Automated; low severity and reversible error</span>]:::hootl

    COMP --> Q1
    Q1 -- "High severity<br/>or irreversible" --> Q2
    Q1 -- "Medium severity<br/>error reversible" --> HOTL
    Q1 -- "Low severity<br/>and reversible" --> HOOTL
    Q2 -- "Yes" --> Q3
    Q2 -- "No" --> FIX
    Q3 -- "Yes" --> HITL
    Q3 -- "No" --> FIX
    FIX --> HITL
    HOTL -. "Upgrade: override rate near zero,<br/>confidence narrows, or new context" .-> HITL
    HOOTL -. "Upgrade: override rate near zero,<br/>confidence narrows, or new context" .-> HOTL

    classDef start    fill:#a5d8ff,stroke:#4a9eed,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef question fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef hitl     fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    classDef hotl     fill:#d0bfff,stroke:#8b5cf6,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef hootl    fill:#b2f2bb,stroke:#22c55e,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef fix      fill:#ffd8d8,stroke:#ef4444,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
